description: Here is the Pirate's first match after her only loss. She had told us she practiced her leg work and that was definitely evident in her crushing defeat of Jade. Jade was undefeated this season, but hit a wall of talent when she rumbled with the Pirate. The Pirate used all kinds of strategies and tricks, and even tried to get the first tickling submission here at US. This was a great victory for the Pirate and another set back for the Trooper.
title: The Pirate (3-1) vs. The Trooper (1-0)
